File containing useful information regarding BLT's mechanics.

AUSTERE:
	- Take "The Old Master" focus and choose it over Persuasive
PERSUASIVE:
	- Take "The Old Master" focus and choose it over Austere
DILIGENT:
	- Complete every focus in any of the 4 starting tree branches, and then take "The Moment of Truth" focus (will also be obtained if focus is bypassed).
BRAVE:
	- Take "Rebuke The Horned Crown's Authority" and successfully end the dream sequence taking the option to fight.

STARTING TREE TRAIT EFFECTS:
PATIENT    - II
TACTICAL   - II
ERUDITE    - II
DILIGENT   - III
PERSUASIVE - III
CONNIVING  - I
HARDENED   - II
BRAVE      - II
AUSTERE    - II
GALLANT    - I

